    <h2>Why I like "Re:Zero - Starting Life in Another World and The Frozen Bond</h2>
    <p class="custom-paragraph">
       I love the series because of the interesting plot and a character, Emilia. Emilia had to go through so much hardship, but she never yielded, she continued to help others just to make a friend, even to people who want to harm her, she is the true and only angel in my heart.
    </p>
    <h2>Characters</h2>
    <h3>Emilia</h3>
    <div class="inline">
      <p class="inline">
         <img src="https://otakuusamagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/frozen-bond-ova.png" width="220">Emilia is an innocent and kind half elf who looks identical to the witch of Envy, Satella, who killed half of the world's population. However, despite all the hatred, she remained kind, dilligent, and temperant, often mapping the parlous Elior forest so nobody will get lost. She also forgives and even risks her life to save people who tried to harm her.
         </div>
    <h3>Puck</h3>
    <div class="inline">
      <p class="inline">
         <img src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/rezero/images/c/cd/Beastoftheend.PNG" width="200"> Puck is a cat like spirit, also called The Beast of The End, one of the 4 great spirits created by the Witch of Greed, Echidna. Puck first found Emilia trapped in a crystal and saved her, he gave her clothes and became her only friend. Puck sees Emilia as his daughter, he even risked his life to save her from another great spirit who wants to kill Emilia, The Arbitrator, Melakuera.
         </div>
    <h3>Melakuera</h3>
    <div class="inline">
      <p class="inline">
         <img src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/villains/images/1/17/Mediator_Melaquera_profile.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20210102222212" width="200">Melakuera is a horse like spirit covered in fire, also called the Arbitrator, created by the Witch of Greed, Echidna. Melakuera believes in extreme justice and viewed Emilia's existence as a sin.
         </div>
